00:00:03.930 --> 00:00:06.740
in this circle and what I wanna prove

00:00:06.740 --> 00:00:09.960
is that for any inscribed quadrilateral,

00:00:09.960 --> 00:00:13.542
that opposite angles are supplementary.

00:00:13.542 --> 00:00:15.857
So when I say they're supplementary,

00:00:15.857 --> 00:00:18.080
the measure of this angle
plus the measure of this angle

00:00:18.080 --> 00:00:19.970
need to be 180 degrees.

00:00:19.970 --> 00:00:22.380
The measure of this angle
plus the measure of this angle

00:00:22.380 --> 00:00:24.412
need to be 180 degrees.

00:00:24.412 --> 00:00:26.650
